    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/b02788b1d4f104d51e3ef26370292180.poster.avif?t=1722267758\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/b02788b1d4f104d51e3ef26370292180.webm?t=1722267758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/b02788b1d4f104d51e3ef26370292180.mp4?t=1722267758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Drag and Drop Medieval</strong> 是一款令人着迷的益智游戏，设定在一个中世纪世界中，您的主要任务是使用鼠标移动角色。这听起来很简单，但游戏提供了超过20个精心设计的关卡，每个关卡都有其独特的挑战和机制。在解决谜题并揭开这个中世纪王国的秘密时，享受迷人的像素艺术图形。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/5b7a903f6bdc4f384a3882b0fda48c5d.poster.avif?t=1722267758\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/5b7a903f6bdc4f384a3882b0fda48c5d.webm?t=1722267758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/5b7a903f6bdc4f384a3882b0fda48c5d.mp4?t=1722267758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直观的拖放机制的引人入胜的游戏玩法:</h2></strong> 简单但引人入胜的游戏玩法，您可以使用鼠标移动中世纪角色。战略思维将每一个动作变成一个脑筋急转弯。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有独特谜题的超过20个挑战性关卡:</h2></strong> 导航超过20个关卡，每个关卡都有独特的谜题，测试您的解决问题的技能，并保持您的娱乐。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >迷人的像素艺术图形:</h2></strong> 享受视觉上吸引人的像素艺术图形，使中世纪的世界栩栩如生，增强游戏的怀旧和身临其境的氛围。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过10种独特的游戏机制:</h2></strong> 掌握各种机制，从移动障碍到解锁路径，每一种都增加了新的复杂性和乐趣。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁5个隐藏成就:</h2></strong> 发现隐藏的秘密并解锁5个成就，奖励您在解决游戏谜题时的创造力和毅力。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/78cd0edfa47ed283972a2850c2aa97cb.poster.avif?t=1722267758\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/78cd0edfa47ed283972a2850c2aa97cb.webm?t=1722267758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028280/extras/78cd0edfa47ed283972a2850c2aa97cb.mp4?t=1722267758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul></li></ul>",
